{"tid":1452791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發文宣] 警犬搞緊軍事政變","createTime":"2019-08-12T02:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:55:56.000Z","uid":66047,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"38a578f3f8afff23488d888ad9222fbcbd2d66f8","tid":1452791,"uid":66047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:22:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">開頭對異政見人仕打壓</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聯同金錢利益建制大黨勾結</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一而再 再而三公然警黑勾結 <span style=\"color: red;\">鄉黑 福建</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">著手公開信反擊政務司長代公開道歉</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">從721到811 警犬無差別打平民大屠殺行刑式追捕</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">顯然香港係沒有任何政制/法制可以控制警犬</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好大機會林奠/各高官係比警犬軟禁<br />\n因而從來冇任何一次公開遣責警犬</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結論警犬係軍事政變！！<br />\n而家已經全權控制緊香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">另盡快搵方法求證前線仲有冇鬼</span></span>"},{"pid":"0fdeb562ec247fa5c9a714b4322d701644858570","tid":1452791,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bccd30ec7cd08dd280ef812f4bacb423f88be57","tid":1452791,"uid":266011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38a578f3f8afff23488d888ad9222fbcbd2d66f8","tid":1452791,"uid":66047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:22:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">開頭對異政見人仕打壓</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聯同金錢利益建制大黨勾結</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一而再 再而三公然警黑勾結 <span style=\"color: red;\">鄉黑 福建</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">著手公開信反擊政務司長代公開道歉</span><br />\n<br />\n<sp